data.description: This home located in Ridgeview at Stetson Hills provides easy access to all things Colorado Springs. Stucco exterior, 3 car garage, backyard with no adjoining backyard neighbors makes this home perfect for lounging, relaxing or hanging out. Inside you'll find plenty of space for your inner chef, space for technology and learning, space for lounging and plenty of bedrooms for privacy and rest.. that's just on the main level and upstairs. The finished basement offers additional space for gaming, entertaining, movie time whatever you envision, plus 2 private bedrooms and a full bathroom! The Master Suite includes a gas fireplace, 5 piece bath and walk-in closet for your own personal retreat. Plenty of windows will let Colorado's natural light in the entire home and the central air conditioner will allow you to stay cool on those warmer days. Close to shopping, schools, and the Powers Corridor.
